      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是HealthTech_PatientRecords，然后连到Still。那Still之后呢？是只能去Moving，还是有其他分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Still有两个去向：一个是进入HealthTech_EMR_Sync做同步，另一个是变成Moving状态。另外Moving和Still之间要双向流转，数据可以来回切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Still到HealthTech_EMR_Sync、Still到Moving、以及Moving和Still之间的双向箭头加上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个关键路径：Moving状态可能会发生Crash，Crash之后数据要进入HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault进行合规存储。这是HIPAA的要求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Moving指向Crash，然后Crash指向HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。Crash是终止状态还是会继续流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
